{"id": "0fee09d396060fae8c24d594cc2710d6", "ts": "1775002036.000000", "text": "Oh. That was us — or rather, that was Vantage Distributed. They began their self-service onboarding on March 21. The first group of about 500 employees started on Monday, with the remaining approximately 700, including contractors, joining by March 23. More than 1,200 users have accessed the portal, uploaded documents, and utilized the relocation matching algorithm.

I did bring this up in #customer-engagement when the deal was finalized on March 18. @Samira even highlighted the potential increase in traffic in that discussion. However, I don’t think anyone assessed the actual impact on infrastructure costs.

