{"id": "b517bc647fa722fc091585aa5ac38f4d", "ts": "1775566020.000000", "text": "The schema validation tests look excellent, Dmitri — I will incorporate them into the pipeline deployment gate in ENG-217. Every configuration deployment must successfully pass `test_config_field_types`, `test_required_fields`, and `test_config_matches_source` before it can enter production.

