{"id": "ea9699892edf99cc39afb2138ce353ea", "ts": "1777122780.000000", "text": "Adding onto Chloe's point: the Terraform coordinator relief Elena mentioned is still not real capacity. As of this morning the role hasn't even been posted, so there is no world where that hire helps us absorb BrightLoop's May wave.

